highlights.text: YUNGTARR has the most spots on Viral Songs Thailand. “OMW” is the highest at #34.
“Catching Bodies” by Sekou is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Thailand at #50.
“One Of My Life” by BLVCKHEART and K6Y has been on Viral Songs Thailand the longest, at 256 days straight.
“คนเบล้อ” by จ้องน้อย หรอยเว่อร์ is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Thailand, up 12 spots at #36.
